flowRoot.flowPara: openSUSE is a free Linux-based operating system for your PC. You can surf the web, manage your e-mails and photos, do office work, play videos or music
This DVD includes everything you need to get your desktop, laptop, or server up
and running with Linux in no time!
Processor: Intel: Pentium 1-4, Xeon or newer; AMD: Duron, Athlon, Athlon XP,MP,64, Sempron, Opteron or newer.
Hard Disk: At least 500MB for minimal system; 2.5GB recommended for standard system.
Graphics and Sound Card: Supports most modern sound and graphics cards.
Be part of the openSUSE community!
The popular GNU Image Manipulation Program is installed by default.

text.tspan: The openSUSE project is a community program sponsored by Novell.

flowRoot.flowPara: This DVD is dual-sided and includes 32-bit software on one side, and 64-bit software on the other.
